This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to extract knowledge from text, which are common topics in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of embeddings, which are a popular technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and databases (cs.DB).
